{"tid":4954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大陸生85%留港就業，月薪高港生2.5倍","createTime":"2016-11-26T16:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T17:29:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8c84d9bf030bbf2e7107797529b8d70f304fad","tid":4954,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:55:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">港大陸生85%留港就業，月薪高港生2.5倍<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=2709# \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D2709%23%20&d=5%2BTcBHUMpf%2Brh3STZOnpZ8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=21eb777c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=2709# </a><br />\n<br />\n近年香港各大專院校多了不少大陸學生，在校園走一圈，<span style=\"color: red;\">聽普通話絕對比廣東話更多</span>。而這些學生當中，大部分都會選擇留港就業，而且<span style=\"color: blue;\">人工往往比港生還要高一截</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：民主黨護航送入香港，<span style=\"color: red;\">共匪黨委及中資情報網絡幫助搵好工，你班香港人子弟，要再努力十倍啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">[過橋抽板]英媒:大陸人:千萬別讓港仔溜進來打工</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://forum15.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6619053&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum15.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6619053%26page%3D1&d=5%2BTcBHUMpf%2Brh3STZOnpZ8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=cef6f06d\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum15.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6619053&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中資行賤招逼走港人</span> <br />\n<br />\n臨近半年結，基金朋友報料，又有大型投行裁員。朋友說：「喂喂，又有大行裁員喇！（個市差到咁，裁員有幾咁奇呀？東亞（023）都裁員啦！）」朋友再說︰「&amp;#21946;&amp;#65533;&amp;#65533;家咁&amp;#22021;時勢，裁員當然唔出奇啦，有&amp;#21874;外資大行個個月都係逐少逐少咁，兩、三個人咁裁，我唔係想講呢&amp;#21874;，我係想話，中資行都裁員喇。」 <br />\n中資行也裁員？中資行不是為拿下香港財金界「話語權」，不停高價招兵買馬嗎？朋友謂，經歷去年大跌市，加上大陸資金「水緊」，原本極具野心的中資行，不能不再檢視在港發展策略，得出需削減香港員工結論。 <br />\n早些看清事實也算好事，但還是那一句，現市況裁員「有幾咁奇」？ <br />\n朋友說：「奇就奇在，中資行唔係用正常方法裁員，係用非常手法，用唔使賠錢&amp;#22021;賤招&hellip;&hellip;若果想炒分析員，就不停逼佢寫&amp;#21874;無用&amp;#22021;報告，或者定個做唔到&amp;#22021;目標，要佢call客call到做到為止。」 <br />\n賤招成功否？朋友說：「好成功，好多香港員工咪頂唔住走晒囉，只係剩番&amp;#21874;平人工內地人。」其實，這會不會才是裁員的真正目的？。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20160606/large/16230120z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160606%2Flarge%2F16230120z.jpg&h=b71880bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n密西比 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20160606/19642744[/quote]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20160606%2F19642744%5B%2Fquote%5D&d=5%2BTcBHUMpf%2Brh3STZOnpZ8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=6f81f9c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20160606%2F19642744%5B%2Fquote%5D&h=8d18efa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20160606/19642744[/quote]</a>"},{"pid":"8cb67fb683543e59af4d69b32e77ef6cddaeb20a","tid":4954,"uid":14099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c6e948aff89483a7cc756dba6b02bfa9a9d99d","tid":4954,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"點解lihkg都仲會有睇content farm嘅on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d33718377e2f9d93e89c17cf078220144f5f4b9","tid":4954,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62285679afc6859a8a3c7ed6e17aa787504bdd55","tid":4954,"uid":1723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"Content farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搏刺激情緒呃hit呃like呃廣告"}]}